	(do_writekey): Follow the change of ecc_writekey.
	(do_auth): Support KEY_TYPE_EDDSA.
	(parse_ecc_curve): Support CURVE_ED25519.  Bug fix for other curves.
	(parse_algorithm_attribute): Bug fix for ECDH.  Support EdDSA.

